PICTURE: ASCII character portrait

Syntax: picture
        picture set
        picture clear
        picture show <player>

DESCRIPTION:
  Store a small ASCII portrait on your character.

  picture              view your own portrait
  picture set          enter a multi-line portrait (. to finish)
  picture clear        remove your portrait
  picture show <name>  view a portrait when that player is in the room

  Limits: 15 lines, 72 characters per line.

SEE ALSO: customize, describe, look
